Henriette "Henni" Forchhammer, onye a makwaara dị ka Margarete Forchham Mer (1863), bụ onye nkuzi Danish, onye na-ahụ maka ụmụ nwanyị na onye na-eme udo.

Amụrụ ya n'afọ 1863 n'aka Johannes Nicolai Georg Forchhammer, nwanne nwanyị nke physicist na onye nkuzi Johannes Georg Forchhanmer na onye na-agụ egwu Viggo Forchham Mer na nwanne nne nke onye nduzi ihe nkiri Bjarne Forchhamer
Ọ bụ nwa nwa Johan Georg Forchhammer na nwa nwa August Friedrich Wilhelm Forchhamber.
Ebenside N'afọ 1899, ọ bụ onye guzobere Danske Kvinders Nationalråd, ọ bụkwa onye otu bọọdụ site na mbido
Ọ bụ onye isi oche nke nzukọ ahụ site n'afọ 1913 ruo n'afọ 1931
O sokwa guzobe Women's International League for Peace and Freedom n'afọ 1915, ọ bụkwa osote onye isi oche nke International Council of Women site n'afọ 1914 ruo n'afọ 1930
Site n'afọ 1920 ruo n'afọ 1937 ọ bụ onye nnọchi anya na Njikọ Mba
